EN: This is my latest signature style.

ZH: 签名是一个人的身份标识。
EN: A signature is an identity symbol for a person.

ZH: 我在画作的右下角签了名。
EN: I signed my name at the bottom right corner of the artwork.

ZH: 这份合同需要亲自在纸上签名。
EN: This contract needs to be personally signed on paper.
